members.name: isCancelled
members.comment: Gets the cancellation state of this event. A cancelled event will not be executed in the server, but will still pass to other plugins

return: true if this event is cancelled

members.name: setCancelled
members.comment: Sets the cancellation state of this event. A cancelled event will not be executed in the server, but will still pass to other plugins.

param: cancel - true if you wish to cancel this event
